@startuml
title Store Order Checkout Sequence

actor "Store Customer" as Customer
participant "Checkout Workspace" as Workspace
participant "Store API" as StoreAPI
database "Order Store" as Orders
database "Inventory" as Inventory

Customer -> Workspace: Review inventory before checkout
' operationId: getInventory
Workspace -> StoreAPI: GET /store/inventory
StoreAPI -> Inventory: Read inventory counts
StoreAPI --> Workspace: Status quantity map

Customer -> Workspace: Submit order
' operationId: placeOrder
Workspace -> StoreAPI: POST /store/order
StoreAPI -> Orders: Persist Order
StoreAPI --> Workspace: Order created

Customer -> Workspace: Confirm order state
' operationId: getOrderById
Workspace -> StoreAPI: GET /store/order/{orderId}
StoreAPI -> Orders: Lookup Order
StoreAPI --> Workspace: Order details

Customer -> Workspace: Cancel invalid order
' operationId: deleteOrder
Workspace -> StoreAPI: DELETE /store/order/{orderId}
StoreAPI -> Orders: Delete Order
StoreAPI --> Workspace: Order deleted
@enduml
